  "title": "Apocalypse Rising",
  "description": "A mod that adds tons of fully modeled, modern melee weapons",
  "body": "<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1215245/description_5964d192-d4a0-4b36-90c4-b4f84c7f8f67.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"943\" height=\"150\"></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://discord.com/invite/U49kcYmZ8U\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/cozy/social/discord-singular_vector.svg\" alt=\"discord-singular\"></a><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/apocalypse-rising\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/cozy/available/curseforge_vector.svg\" alt=\"modrinth\"></a></p>\n<h1 id=\"about\">About</h1>\n<p><strong>A mod that adds tons of fully modeled, modern melee weapons</strong></p>\n<h1 id=\"features\">Features</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>Detailed 3D weapon models</li>\n<li>Fully data driven weapon crafting</li>\n<li>Unique weapons</li>\n<li>Fully compatible with Better Combat</li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"httpsmediaforgecdnnetattachmentsdescription1215245description_26e4b8ce-55d1-4c15-93d5-1889929a6928pnghttpswwwkinetichostingnet\"><a href=\"https://www.kinetichosting.net/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1215245/description_26e4b8ce-55d1-4c15-93d5-1889929a6928.png\" alt=\"\"></a></h1>\n<h1 id=\"feedback\">Feedback</h1>\n<p>Let me now about features and weapons you want to see in the mod in the comments. This will help me a lot, thanks. Also you can join my discord to share you feedback there.</p>\n<h1 id=\"dependencies\">Dependencies</h1>\n<p>📩<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/curios\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Curios API(Required)</a></p>\n<p>📩<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/better-combat-by-daedelus\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Better Combat(Optional)</a></p>\n<p>📩<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/jei\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">JEI(For viewing recipes, optional)</a></p>\n<h1 id=\"roadmap\">Roadmap</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>Epic Fight compatibility</li>\n<li>More weapons</li>\n<li>Weapon customization(different skins for weapons)</li>\n<li>Armor</li>\n<li>Food</li>\n<li>More decorative blocks</li>\n<li>A standalone mod/texturepack for backpacks</li>\n<li>Some more misc stuff</li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"contributors\">Contributors</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>@neon</a>_a_who(Wooden Board Barricade model)</li>\n</ul>",
